snippet.title: Sherrilyn Dale
snippet.description: Oh Hi! Im Sherrilyn and I'm so glad you found me! If you're into True Crime, Makeup, Beauty Reviews and Hauls (you know, the essentials) than you have come to the right place! Must accept awkward moments, my inability to form most basic sentences and casual appearances by the people closest to me! If all this sounds up your alley come join the fam! XO Sher
